                            <comment id="13588875" author="lewismc" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2013 22:53:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch cleans up (and satisfies) my initial problem with this issue. My suggestion to add the Feed.java class has been dropped. Typically one will utilize some other existing vocabulary (already within Apache Tika) to represent fields their Metadata fields in a more consistent way. This is OK and I am happy with this.&lt;br/&gt;
